{
  "stem": "7437.2",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And I ended up in the neighboring fields, wheat fields, that were ready for harvest because it was harvest time.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And there I spend the next two days trying to sort out what I have to do.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "By that time, the bread and the apple were gone.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And I decided again that he probably refused to let my mother in.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And she ran through the forest looking for me.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And so I thought, at that time, that I must find my mother.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And the only way I could find my mother would be going to the forest.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "The area where I come from is-- I mean-- I mean, there are forests all over the place.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And that's what I decided to do.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "It wasn't really by choice.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "That was the only place one could hide.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "In the very first months of my odyssey, I encountered many stragglers from neighboring ghettos.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "Apparently, the ghettos were liquidated in our area of Poland about the same time.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "It was before our high holidays of 1942.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "There were many encounters in the early days.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "And we tried to compare, you know, our information and asking for information-- whether or not, perhaps, they've met some of our family or, or friends.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "I never met anyone who met any of my friends or my family.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "One time, there were seven of us.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "And that was about three months after the liquidation of our ghetto-- was already in the fall.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "There were seven of us sitting at the edge of a forest.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "And there was one baby, a mother and a baby, and a little boy, and then adolescents, and two older people.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "We were comparing notes.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "And all of a sudden, a group of children from the village, from the neighboring village, spotted us.",
      "word_count": 18
    }
  ],
